<div id="review_2083927390" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2083927390" />
    <a title="Sophie Levy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16434181-sophie-levy"><img alt="Sophie Levy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1358183132p2/16434181.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2083927390?book_show_action=true">Aug 06, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sophie Levy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sophie Levy" href="/user/show/16434181-sophie-levy">Sophie Levy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2083927390" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2001071473514414362">Dans un mois, dans un an, comment souffrirons-nous, Seigneur, que tant de mers me séparent de vous? Que le jour commence et que le jour finisse, sans que jamais Titus ne revoie Berenice, sans que de tout le jour je ne revoie Titus?</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

